title: Change Your Beliefs

description:
Episode 469 - The world seems to be more divided than ever. The reason why is because people hold their beliefs too tightly. In order for your life to change and in order for the world to change we must change what we believe. Today were gonna talk about how to change your beliefs so that you can be successful.
